[Follow Your Heart]

3
00:01:51,330 --> 00:01:54,050
[Episode 18]

4
00:02:00,270 --> 00:02:00,710
Boss.

5
00:02:01,110 --> 00:02:01,580
Boss!

6
00:02:01,750 --> 00:02:02,229
Boss.

7
00:02:02,750 --> 00:02:04,150
Why's the princess here?

8
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:05,710
Well...

9
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:06,710
Since you'd decided

10
00:02:06,710 --> 00:02:07,970
against the marriage,

11
00:02:07,970 --> 00:02:09,480
why did you mock her?

12
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:11,070
I didn't.

13
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:11,710
Sai'er.

14
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:12,950
With Ruoqian,

15
00:02:12,950 --> 00:02:14,630
kindly ask the customers to leave.

16
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:16,830
Tell them we're closing early

17
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:17,890
as I'm sick.

18
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:18,790
Okay.

19
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:20,020
I'll go now.

20
00:02:20,230 --> 00:02:20,550
Go.

21
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,210
So you purposely bullied her?

22
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:23,110
Pei Yaoyao...

23
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:23,850
I'm sorry.

24
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:25,440
We're closing early today.

25
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,829
Come again next time.

26
00:02:27,910 --> 00:02:29,430
How dare you call her ugly?

27
00:02:29,790 --> 00:02:30,190
You...

28
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,070
Look at you now.

29
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:33,160
Are you fit

30
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:34,670
to be one of the Jiangs?

31
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:39,800
This is not an ordinary blind date.

32
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:42,390
It concerns your prospects and future.

33
00:02:42,780 --> 00:02:43,550
Don't you know

34
00:02:43,550 --> 00:02:45,070
your situation's precarious?

35
00:02:45,070 --> 00:02:46,630
Without Grand Councilor Pei's protection,

36
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:47,990
how can you stay safe?

37
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,670
Mr. Pei might not dare

38
00:02:50,270 --> 00:02:51,940
help me too.

39
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:53,790
What’s more,

40
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,829
he has to give up

41
00:02:54,829 --> 00:02:56,160
his precious daughter.

42
00:02:56,230 --> 00:02:57,360
You're too willful.

43
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,780
You’ve been

44
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,130
stubborn in Heman once.

45
00:03:01,270 --> 00:03:02,400
Your first marriage

46
00:03:02,829 --> 00:03:03,950
was reckless.

47
00:03:04,230 --> 00:03:05,390
I didn't pursue it.

48
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:07,250
No matter what,

49
00:03:07,390 --> 00:03:08,840
I must make sure your second marriage

50
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,990
doesn't go wrong.

51
00:03:12,670 --> 00:03:14,400
You offended all the officials

52
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:16,690
with your Zornia investigation.

53
00:03:16,830 --> 00:03:19,150
I tried to persuade you, but you didn't listen.

54
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,210
I know that with my power,

55
00:03:20,210 --> 00:03:21,450
I can't protect you.

56
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,470
You can only let Mr. Pei

57
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:24,190
protect you

58
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:25,590
through marriage.

59
00:03:27,790 --> 00:03:29,390
I don't want my marriage to be

60
00:03:30,070 --> 00:03:31,520
tied down by interests.

61
00:03:32,230 --> 00:03:33,870
Such a burdensome marriage

62
00:03:34,350 --> 00:03:35,680
can't protect me at all.

63
00:03:36,670 --> 00:03:37,470
How?

64
00:03:41,829 --> 00:03:42,470
My father

65
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:44,820
was exiled and killed.

66
00:03:45,550 --> 00:03:47,550
His marriage failed to protect him.

67
00:04:01,110 --> 00:04:02,710
I was careless with my words.

68
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:07,270
When will you

69
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:08,510
become sensible?

70
00:04:47,110 --> 00:04:47,710
You...

71
00:04:55,970 --> 00:04:59,670
[Fanhou Street]

72
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:03,430
Mr. Li.

73
00:05:03,909 --> 00:05:05,830
Our shop's about to be ruined

74
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:06,760
by the constables.

75
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,760
Your father's nonchalant about it.

76
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,260
What...

77
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:10,340
What should we do?

78
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:11,870
I'm not his real son.

79
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:14,140
Though my mom had me in an affair,

80
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:16,390
my grandfather's a high-ranking official.

81
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,550
What can Li Jun do?

82
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,120
He has to

83
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:20,560
accept being a cuckold.

84
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:23,190
I have to tell Lord Lu about this,

85
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,630
so he can support you.

86
00:05:25,150 --> 00:05:25,790
Support?

87
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:27,430
I'm a maternal

88
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:28,710
grandson.

89
00:05:29,350 --> 00:05:30,250
All these years,

90
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:31,590
my grandfather left the dirty work

91
00:05:31,590 --> 00:05:32,390
to me,

92
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,190
while his dear grandson Lu Bo'an

93
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:35,660
is studying in Imperial Academy

94
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:37,520
to become a pillar of the country.

95
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:39,830
In times of peace,

96
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,590
all is just and fair.

97
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:44,730
When the Lu family's endangered,

98
00:05:45,590 --> 00:05:47,110
I'll be the one abandoned.

99
00:05:49,030 --> 00:05:50,360
Who is sneaking around?

100
00:05:54,110 --> 00:05:54,800
What's going on?

101
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,230
Boss.

102
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,990
Someone was eavesdropping.

103
00:05:57,490 --> 00:05:58,020
Get them.

104
00:05:58,230 --> 00:05:58,710
Yes.

105
00:06:00,909 --> 00:06:02,390
[Closed]

106
00:06:26,130 --> 00:06:27,070
Why did you

107
00:06:27,230 --> 00:06:28,630
ask Sai'er to call me over

108
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:29,790
at this late hour?

109
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:31,780
There's someone to meet.

110
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:55,430
Mr. Jiang.

111
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:57,750
How have you been?

112
00:07:06,030 --> 00:07:06,710
General Nan.

113
00:07:06,710 --> 00:07:08,070
You sure are something.

114
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,640
I searched everywhere,

115
00:07:11,150 --> 00:07:11,990
only for you

116
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:13,160
to be hiding

117
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,230
under my nose.

118
00:07:25,790 --> 00:07:27,190
He's a general after all.

119
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:28,870
Is this how you

120
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,710
treat guests from afar?

121
00:07:33,150 --> 00:07:35,440
He's a fugitive.

122
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:37,550
I'm willing to take him in

123
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:38,860
and hide him.

124
00:07:39,210 --> 00:07:41,070
What's wrong with doing some work

125
00:07:41,110 --> 00:07:42,140
in return?

126
00:07:42,930 --> 00:07:44,130
If you're concerned,

127
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:45,800
you can do it for him.

128
00:07:55,140 --> 00:07:56,070
Wipe them clean.

129
00:08:06,430 --> 00:08:09,090
-An imperial criminal?
-An imperial criminal?

130
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,630
Lower your voice.

131
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:12,690
Don’t get implicated.

132
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,630
If you took him in,

133
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:17,140
he mustn't be rotten.

134
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:18,720
Even if he is

135
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,980
an imperial criminal,

136
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:21,390
he must be wronged.

137
00:08:21,990 --> 00:08:23,550
We trust you, Boss.

138
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:24,630
You really

139
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:25,750
trust me so much?

140
00:08:26,590 --> 00:08:27,270
Of course.

141
00:08:27,290 --> 00:08:28,550
I'll always trust you.

142
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,230
In that case,

143
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:33,350
Keep it a secret, okay?

144
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,490
Rumor has it that

145
00:08:51,110 --> 00:08:52,310
you went to the South.

146
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:54,760
I was still guessing

147
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:55,870
which of the six

148
00:08:56,350 --> 00:08:58,350
Southern countries you could be in.

149
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:00,960
I started

150
00:09:00,990 --> 00:09:02,000
the rumor...

151
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:04,480
to be inconspicuous

152
00:09:05,540 --> 00:09:06,350
and sneak back

153
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:07,570
to the capital.

154
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:12,790
Why didn’t you

155
00:09:12,790 --> 00:09:14,030
come look for me?

156
00:09:15,710 --> 00:09:16,710
Why should I trust

157
00:09:16,710 --> 00:09:18,310
a man who can't keep his word?

158
00:09:19,310 --> 00:09:20,240
What do you mean?

159
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:21,710
What do you think?

160
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:28,650
Explain my crime first

161
00:09:28,990 --> 00:09:30,250
before convicting me.

162
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:32,670
You said

163
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:36,050
you'd keep investigating in the capital.

164
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:38,670
But not long after you left,

165
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:39,670
Heman's magistrate and lieutenant

166
00:09:39,670 --> 00:09:41,080
were replaced.

167
00:09:42,010 --> 00:09:43,780
They soon became allies

168
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:44,750
with

169
00:09:44,770 --> 00:09:45,770
Gongye and Tumen,

170
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:47,560
gaining greater momentum.

171
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:49,220
They even framed me

172
00:09:49,260 --> 00:09:50,540
for embezzlement,

173
00:09:51,430 --> 00:09:52,690
forcing me to run away.

174
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,360
You should know they were

175
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:57,290
sent by the Ministry of Personnel.

176
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,950
The Ministry of Personnel assigns

177
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:03,410
officials to their posts.

178
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:06,080
What?

179
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,350
Are you suspecting me?

180
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:12,350
At first,

181
00:10:13,230 --> 00:10:14,070
I did.

182
00:10:17,430 --> 00:10:18,710
Then why are you

183
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:19,940
looking for me now?

184
00:10:23,970 --> 00:10:25,150
I know you solved

185
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,950
the Ghost Market's Zornia case,

186
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,210
eliminating a Zornia cartel

187
00:10:28,210 --> 00:10:29,400
in the capital.

188
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:43,430
Just because the magistrate and lieutenant

189
00:10:43,430 --> 00:10:44,960
were recommended by Li Jun,

190
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,950
you suspect he

191
00:10:47,350 --> 00:10:48,990
and even the entire Ministry of Personnel

192
00:10:48,990 --> 00:10:51,010
are overseeing the Zornia business?

193
00:10:51,010 --> 00:10:52,810
As those two started framing me,

194
00:10:52,870 --> 00:10:54,190
Li Jun went to His Majesty

195
00:10:54,190 --> 00:10:55,390
to complain about me.

196
00:10:56,950 --> 00:10:58,480
Is that just a coincidence?

197
00:10:59,620 --> 00:11:00,510
Over the years,

198
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:01,960
all officials were

199
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:02,710
sent to Heman

200
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:04,870
through the Ministry of Personnel.

201
00:11:06,190 --> 00:11:07,130
They're sealing off

202
00:11:07,130 --> 00:11:07,890
a path.

203
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:20,030
I want to meet His Majesty,

204
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,840
but I haven't found a chance.

205
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:28,110
You're now a guilty official

206
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:29,240
who's running away.

207
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:30,850
Without evidence,

208
00:11:31,110 --> 00:11:32,240
it's just nonsense.

209
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:34,530
His Majesty will only punish you.

210
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:36,370
It's not the right time

211
00:11:36,950 --> 00:11:37,790
to meet him.

212
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,930
I know you're also watching the Li family.

213
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:43,620
How did you know?

214
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:45,190
We met when I was undercover

215
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:46,210
in the Lis' casino

216
00:11:46,310 --> 00:11:47,240
to get evidence.

217
00:11:47,710 --> 00:11:49,170
You didn't expose me then.

218
00:11:49,830 --> 00:11:50,550
I guess you hoped

219
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:51,680
I'd find something.

220
00:11:57,180 --> 00:11:57,910
Somewhat.

221
00:11:58,660 --> 00:12:00,030
Come on, I bet you

222
00:12:00,310 --> 00:12:01,840
just didn't recognize him.

223
00:12:06,940 --> 00:12:07,590
So...

224
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:09,850
what've you found out?

225
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,280
I'm only cleared of half

226
00:12:12,310 --> 00:12:13,640
of my suspicions of you.

227
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:15,560
I'll tell you when they are

228
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:16,510
all cleared.

229
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:20,260
Fine.

230
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:23,750
I want to go

231
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,280
see Bieli first.

232
00:12:26,430 --> 00:12:27,150
I know you two

233
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:28,270
had a misunderstanding,

234
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,400
so I didn't go to him,

235
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:31,680
in case I'd add fuel to the fire.

236
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:33,470
You can't see him now.

237
00:12:33,950 --> 00:12:34,420
Why?

238
00:12:35,710 --> 00:12:36,710
He might be

239
00:12:36,710 --> 00:12:38,240
related to the Zornia case.

240
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:39,510
Some Jinwu Guards

241
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:40,910
are dealing with Zornia.

242
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:42,350
Impossible!

243
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:44,910
She saw it too.

244
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:51,070
He's too close to the Li family.

245
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,870
I've to be wary of him.

246
00:12:55,310 --> 00:12:56,550
Evidence aside,

247
00:12:57,150 --> 00:12:59,210
what you saw might not be true either.

248
00:12:59,810 --> 00:13:00,950
Even if you put the evidence

249
00:13:00,950 --> 00:13:01,830
in front of me,

250
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,170
I'd still believe him.

251
00:13:06,330 --> 00:13:07,280
Why do you

252
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:08,550
trust him so much?

253
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:12,630
We have a deep brotherly bond.

254
00:13:14,390 --> 00:13:15,470
We've experienced

255
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:18,440
near-death situations together.

256
00:13:19,630 --> 00:13:20,910
But people change.

257
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:23,190
Sometimes, trust

258
00:13:23,950 --> 00:13:24,950
can't be

259
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:26,550
explained.

260
00:13:29,110 --> 00:13:29,870
But I only

261
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:31,910
believe in evidence.

262
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:43,240
General Nan.

263
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,400
You’re guilty now.

264
00:13:45,770 --> 00:13:46,780
If Commander Shang

265
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:47,910
knows what happened to you

266
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:49,150
and wants to avenge you,

267
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:50,370
we can't stop him.

268
00:13:51,110 --> 00:13:52,310
Right now,

269
00:13:52,990 --> 00:13:54,670
you should hide for a while

270
00:13:55,190 --> 00:13:56,390
before we make plans.

271
00:13:59,580 --> 00:14:00,290
Then

272
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:03,390
I’ll have to disturb you for a while, Dr. Yan.

273
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:09,030
Y-You want to stay here?

274
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:12,950
My... My place is very shabby.

275
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:14,740
I don't mind.

276
00:14:14,950 --> 00:14:15,620
I do.

277
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,540
Her home's too far away.

278
00:14:23,540 --> 00:14:26,600
It inconveniences your investigation in the capital.

279
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,670
Then I'll stay at your place.

280
00:14:30,670 --> 00:14:31,550
No way.

281
00:14:35,810 --> 00:14:37,980
I'm not used to living with others.

282
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:41,080
Where should I live then?

283
00:14:44,190 --> 00:14:44,990
How about...

284
00:14:46,380 --> 00:14:48,310
he stays in Yuejiang's Residence?

285
00:14:48,510 --> 00:14:50,430
Your mother won't betray you.

286
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:51,430
Besides,

287
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,790
no one would dare search Yuejiang's Residence.

288
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:54,230
Right?

289
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:58,020
But my mother and I

290
00:14:58,750 --> 00:14:59,710
just had a fight.

291
00:15:00,590 --> 00:15:02,920
There's no grudge between mother and son.

292
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:03,870
Look.

293
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:06,130
It's a good chance to make up with her.

294
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:13,170
That's a good idea.

295
00:15:15,630 --> 00:15:17,290
You sure accept help readily.

296
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:23,000
It's settled then.

297
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:27,740
[Yuejiang's Residence]

298
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:29,630
General Nan, don't worry.

299
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,780
I will protect you.

