00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:55,470
and gets out of here.

601
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:56,800
The sooner, the better.

602
00:27:57,830 --> 00:27:58,710
I know you're resourceful.

603
00:27:58,710 --> 00:27:59,920
Don't tell me you can't.

604
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:00,760
You can, right?

605
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:01,590
Don't worry, Mother.

606
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:02,580
You must get it done.

607
00:28:02,580 --> 00:28:03,230
Leave it to me.

608
00:28:03,230 --> 00:28:03,380
Okay.

609
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:04,580
You'll be satisfied.

610
00:28:04,730 --> 00:28:06,160
This fan's useless.

611
00:28:06,180 --> 00:28:07,060
I'm so hot.

612
00:28:07,090 --> 00:28:08,400
I'm so angry!

613
00:28:13,190 --> 00:28:15,110
I've bought this house.

614
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:17,110
Please move out

615
00:28:17,670 --> 00:28:18,670
in a day.

616
00:28:21,190 --> 00:28:22,850
Here's the compensation fee.

617
00:28:24,750 --> 00:28:25,390
Fine.

618
00:28:25,910 --> 00:28:27,100
I still have Blossom Beauty.

619
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:28,960
I've also bought Blossom Beauty.

620
00:28:30,230 --> 00:28:31,510
Please move out of it

621
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:32,950
in a day too.

622
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:34,880
You're Imperial Academy's chancellor,

623
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,710
yet you resort to such dirty tricks.

624
00:28:36,710 --> 00:28:37,550
Ms. Yan.

625
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,040
I've already told you that

626
00:28:39,430 --> 00:28:41,060
since you're my brother's friend,

627
00:28:41,060 --> 00:28:42,340
you aren't my friend.

628
00:28:42,830 --> 00:28:44,160
If you aren't my friend,

629
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:45,280
you're my enemy.

630
00:28:45,870 --> 00:28:47,390
You chose it yourself.

631
00:28:49,750 --> 00:28:50,480
Luckily,

632
00:28:50,990 --> 00:28:52,430
I chose to be friends

633
00:28:52,450 --> 00:28:53,510
with your brother.

634
00:28:53,590 --> 00:28:54,450
He's stubborn,

635
00:28:54,470 --> 00:28:55,310
but he isn't

636
00:28:55,710 --> 00:28:57,910
indiscriminate and spiteful like you.

637
00:28:58,570 --> 00:28:59,750
As an outsider,

638
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,480
you have no right to compare us.

639
00:29:04,230 --> 00:29:05,360
If I can't stay here,

640
00:29:05,910 --> 00:29:07,370
I'll find someplace else.

641
00:29:07,560 --> 00:29:08,440
With money,

642
00:29:08,470 --> 00:29:10,510
I won't have trouble finding a place.

643
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:11,830
I'm afraid no one here

644
00:29:12,270 --> 00:29:13,990
would dare be your landlord.

645
00:29:15,390 --> 00:29:16,030
Ms. Yan.

646
00:29:16,390 --> 00:29:17,390
The world is vast.

647
00:29:18,220 --> 00:29:20,020
Why don't you go somewhere else?

648
00:29:20,910 --> 00:29:22,310
Don’t you worry about me.

649
00:29:22,990 --> 00:29:24,550
This is still my home today.

650
00:29:25,230 --> 00:29:25,890
Your Grace,

651
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,290
I won't send you off.

652
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:31,670
Take your time to pack up.

653
00:29:34,430 --> 00:29:35,150
I forgot.

654
00:29:36,390 --> 00:29:38,710
There are many people in the capital lately.

655
00:29:38,710 --> 00:29:40,110
The inns are all full.

656
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:42,520
It won't be easy to find a place.

657
00:29:46,910 --> 00:29:48,190
Bullying with your power!

658
00:29:48,190 --> 00:29:49,920
One bad apple spoils the bunch!

659
00:30:00,470 --> 00:30:02,150
That's the situation.

660
00:30:03,190 --> 00:30:04,070
We'll be closed

661
00:30:04,510 --> 00:30:05,670
for the time being.

662
00:30:06,150 --> 00:30:07,480
Not necessarily, Boss.

663
00:30:10,130 --> 00:30:11,860
I've written three petitions.

664
00:30:12,310 --> 00:30:14,260
Report this to the Ministry of Revenue.

665
00:30:13,080 --> 00:30:14,100
[To: Ministry of Revenue
From: Liu Ruoqian]

666
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:17,070
Report this to the Ministry of Personnel.

667
00:30:15,700 --> 00:30:17,140
[To: Ministry of Personnel
From: Liu Ruoqian]

668
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:18,550
And this one

669
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:20,140
[To: His Majesty
From: Liu Ruoqian]

670
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:20,630
can be presented to His Majesty.

671
00:30:20,750 --> 00:30:23,230
Although I haven't figured out

672
00:30:23,270 --> 00:30:24,870
how I'd get it to His Majesty,

673
00:30:25,390 --> 00:30:27,120
we can't sit back and do nothing

674
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,470
and let these nobles

675
00:30:28,470 --> 00:30:29,510
bully us.

676
00:30:30,670 --> 00:30:31,430
Ruoqian.

677
00:30:31,990 --> 00:30:33,640
This is too troublesome.

678
00:30:34,150 --> 00:30:34,630
Boss.

679
00:30:34,830 --> 00:30:35,470
Let's take

680
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:36,750
the efficient route.

681
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:37,950
Tonight,

682
00:30:37,970 --> 00:30:39,750
I'll sneak into Duke's residence.

683
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:40,430
With

684
00:30:40,970 --> 00:30:41,740
this blade

685
00:30:41,760 --> 00:30:43,200
on the Princess' neck,

686
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,400
she'll stop messing with us.

687
00:30:52,190 --> 00:30:53,150
Boss.

688
00:30:55,070 --> 00:30:56,430
Sai'er, Ruoqian.

689
00:30:57,270 --> 00:30:58,600
These are your salaries

690
00:30:58,790 --> 00:31:00,190
for this and next month.

691
00:31:01,110 --> 00:31:01,840
Keep it well.

692
00:31:02,350 --> 00:31:03,750
It’s enough for a while.

693
00:31:04,760 --> 00:31:05,660
Wait, Boss.

694
00:31:05,950 --> 00:31:07,510
We haven't worked for it yet.

695
00:31:07,510 --> 00:31:08,670
How can we accept it?

696
00:31:08,790 --> 00:31:09,290
Take it back.

697
00:31:09,290 --> 00:31:09,810
Yes.

698
00:31:10,070 --> 00:31:11,600
We can't accept this money.

699
00:31:11,620 --> 00:31:12,790
Take it.

700
00:31:15,590 --> 00:31:17,510
Just take it.

701
00:31:17,990 --> 00:31:19,350
Don’t look down on me.

702
00:31:19,550 --> 00:31:20,260
Do I give in

703
00:31:20,260 --> 00:31:21,230
that easily?

704
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:22,590
Spend this money

705
00:31:22,590 --> 00:31:23,150
slowly.

706
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:24,280
In a few days,

707
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:25,790
you'd have to return to work.

708
00:31:25,790 --> 00:31:27,390
I'll reopen Blossom Beauty.

709
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,310
Then

710
00:31:29,110 --> 00:31:31,060
where'd you be at these days?

711
00:31:31,270 --> 00:31:32,400
Where are you going?

712
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:34,510
Me?

713
00:31:35,950 --> 00:31:37,060
I have money.

714
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:39,660
I won't have trouble finding a place.

715
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:45,930
[Closed]

716
00:32:13,940 --> 00:32:15,000
I know everything.

717
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,670
Did you find a place to go?

718
00:32:21,910 --> 00:32:24,030
If you won't answer, it means no.

719
00:32:29,230 --> 00:32:30,230
Come home with me.

720
00:32:31,830 --> 00:32:32,550
Why?

721
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:35,350
Yan Nanxing.

722
00:32:38,150 --> 00:32:39,480
For my mother and sister's

723
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,590
bullying,

724
00:32:40,830 --> 00:32:42,030
I'll make it up to you.

725
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:44,010
Hide in my residence first

726
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:45,420
so my mother

727
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:46,750
won't come to you again.

728
00:32:46,750 --> 00:32:48,640
Leave the rest to me.

729
00:32:50,580 --> 00:32:52,240
Why should you make it up to me?

730
00:32:52,390 --> 00:32:53,650
You did nothing wrong.

731
00:32:54,230 --> 00:32:54,990
Besides,

732
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:56,790
we're not related.

733
00:32:57,110 --> 00:32:57,870
If someone

734
00:32:58,120 --> 00:32:59,090
sees me in your home,

735
00:32:59,090 --> 00:33:00,550
it'll complicate things.

736
00:33:00,830 --> 00:33:01,560
Yan Nanxing.

737
00:33:05,470 --> 00:33:07,350
I've been busy with the Zornia case.

738
00:33:07,350 --> 00:33:08,070
I didn't take care

739
00:33:08,070 --> 00:33:09,460
of your conflict with my mother.

740
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:10,260
I'm sorry.

741
00:33:12,390 --> 00:33:13,500
Just lie low

742
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:15,270
at my place for a while.

743
00:33:15,830 --> 00:33:16,990
After this period,

744
00:33:17,610 --> 00:33:19,270
I'll give you an explanation.

745
00:33:21,670 --> 00:33:22,190
Well...

746
00:33:23,430 --> 00:33:24,960
if I'm living there for free,

747
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,090
am I under your care?

748
00:33:29,600 --> 00:33:30,400
Yes.

749
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:52,030
[Blossom Beauty]

750
00:33:56,780 --> 00:33:57,790
We haven't heard

751
00:33:57,870 --> 00:33:59,630
from Yan Nanxing these days.

752
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:00,940
She must've

753
00:34:02,150 --> 00:34:03,560
left the capital.

754
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:08,430
Has she really left?

755
00:34:09,910 --> 00:34:10,630
Isn't this

756
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:11,630
what you want?

757
00:34:15,590 --> 00:34:16,100
Yes.

758
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,760
My heart's at ease now.

759
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:22,070
Mother.

760
00:34:22,739 --> 00:34:24,739
I helped you chase away Yan Nanxing.

761
00:34:25,110 --> 00:34:27,350
So, you must promise me one thing.

762
00:34:27,870 --> 00:34:28,469
What is it?

763
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:33,110
Nan Jifeng.

764
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:37,270
N-No.

765
00:34:46,909 --> 00:34:47,510
Suoluo.

766
00:34:47,949 --> 00:34:49,550
Why did you ask me here today?

767
00:34:50,190 --> 00:34:51,190
To see someone.

768
00:34:55,870 --> 00:34:56,469
Brother?

769
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:57,750
Brother!

770
00:35:01,780 --> 00:35:02,380
Bieli?

771
00:35:05,230 --> 00:35:06,870
I won't disturb

772
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:07,950
your reunion.

773
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,020
Brother.

774
00:35:11,810 --> 00:35:12,610
Does Mr. Jiang

775
00:35:13,670 --> 00:35:14,930
know about your visit?

776
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:17,650
He doesn't need to.

777
00:35:18,150 --> 00:35:20,000
Brother, I'll take you away.

778
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:23,320
But now, I'm...

779
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,060
Brother, he killed...

780
00:35:25,660 --> 00:35:27,120
Why do you still trust him?

781
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:29,070
Gaya did die

782
00:35:29,750 --> 00:35:31,210
by Jiang Xinbai's weapon.

783
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,310
But he

784
00:35:33,310 --> 00:35:34,190
didn't

785
00:35:34,620 --> 00:35:35,430
kill her.

786
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,830
Gaya only committed suicide

787
00:35:37,830 --> 00:35:38,900
to escape conviction

788
00:35:38,900 --> 00:35:40,090
to protect me.

789
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:47,130
So that was what happened?

790
00:35:50,350 --> 00:35:50,910
Bieli.

791
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,470
I heard from Mr. Jiang

792
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:56,990
that you're close to Li Jun's family

793
00:35:57,710 --> 00:35:58,230
and that

794
00:35:58,230 --> 00:36:00,390
there are Jinwu Guards dealing with Zornia.

795
00:36:00,390 --> 00:36:01,350
Be honest.

796
00:36:02,070 --> 00:36:02,870
Is that true?

797
00:36:03,790 --> 00:36:05,390
It's just slander.

798
00:36:07,220 --> 00:36:08,350
I saw with my own eyes

799
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:09,270
that he had a meal

800
00:36:09,270 --> 00:36:10,800
with Lu Dingzhao and Li Jun.

801
00:36:11,110 --> 00:36:12,240
What was that about?

802
00:36:16,990 --> 00:36:17,590
Brother.

803
00:36:18,990 --> 00:36:19,850
Do you trust me?

804
00:36:21,030 --> 00:36:22,070
Of course I do.

805
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:23,550
Then come with me.

806
00:36:24,550 --> 00:36:25,420
As for Jinwu Guards

807
00:36:25,420 --> 00:36:26,620
dealing with Zornia,

808
00:36:26,910 --> 00:36:27,830
I'll conduct

809
00:36:28,030 --> 00:36:29,090
an investigation.

810
00:36:29,910 --> 00:36:30,770
Let's consider

811
00:36:31,510 --> 00:36:33,170
other matters in the long run.

812
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,110
Suoluo.

813
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:50,610
I’ll take him away.

814
00:36:50,990 --> 00:36:52,590
If Jiang Xinbai gives you a hard time,

815
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:53,720
ask him to come to me.

816
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:55,390
I can handle

817
00:36:55,390 --> 00:36:56,650
something so trivial.

818
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:57,680
However,

819
00:36:58,150 --> 00:36:59,800
you must hide General Nan well.

820
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:00,500
Don't let anyone

821
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:01,760
know his whereabouts,

822
00:37:01,910 --> 00:37:02,710
including me.

823
00:37:03,510 --> 00:37:05,100
You two must decide carefully

824
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:06,190
when's the best time

825
00:37:06,190 --> 00:37:07,450
to let His Majesty know

826
00:37:07,630 --> 00:37:09,630
that General Nan's in the capital.

827
00:37:10,030 --> 00:37:10,470
Got it.

828
00:37:10,890 --> 00:37:11,710
Thank you.

829
00:37:26,910 --> 00:37:27,570
Delicious.

830
00:37:28,270 --> 00:37:29,130
Not bad, right?

831
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:38,210
I said I'll take care of you.

832
00:37:38,510 --> 00:37:40,440
Why are you still working outside?

833
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:41,830
I had to deliver goods

834
00:37:41,950 --> 00:37:43,460
to some regular customers.

835
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:44,920
Blossom Beauty's closed,

836
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:45,800
but I've to maintain

837
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:46,800
my customer base.

838
00:37:47,190 --> 00:37:47,970
Didn't I tell you

839
00:37:47,970 --> 00:37:49,300
not to go out for a while?

840
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,360
What if Mother finds out

841
00:37:51,390 --> 00:37:52,990
you're still in the capital?

842
00:37:55,470 --> 00:37:57,270
Those regulars won't betray me.

843
00:37:58,470 --> 00:37:59,310
Don't worry.

844
00:37:59,670 --> 00:38:01,510
I won't cause us any trouble.

845
00:38:01,870 --> 00:38:03,270
Have some bamboo shoots.

846
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:05,960
Eat more. Here.

847
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:09,760
My lord.

848
00:38:14,640 --> 00:38:15,880
S-Should I hide?

849
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:16,950
It's Yao.

850
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:18,430
He knows you're here.

851
00:38:25,430 --> 00:38:26,230
What's wrong?

852
00:38:27,030 --> 00:38:28,580
The guards of Yuejiang's Residence reported that

853
00:38:28,580 --> 00:38:30,440
Shang Bieli took Nan Jifeng away.

854
00:38:32,390 --> 00:38:33,200
Where to?

855
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,580
Our men lost them.

856
00:38:39,830 --> 00:38:40,910
Did Suoluo

857
00:38:41,020 --> 00:38:42,350
bring Shang Bieli home?

858
00:38:52,740 --> 00:38:53,580
Keep eating.

859
00:38:54,180 --> 00:38:54,980
Don't go out.

860
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:22,730
[Imperial Academy]

861
00:39:37,590 --> 00:39:38,650
Xinbai, it's late.

862
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:40,040
What brings you here?

863
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:42,990
Where's Nan Jifeng?

864
00:39:46,710 --> 00:39:47,440
I don't know.

865
00:39:48,030 --> 00:39:48,920
Jiang Suoluo.

866
00:39:49,860 --> 00:39:51,120
Why are you doing this?

867
00:39:54,750 --> 00:39:55,870
To you,

868
00:39:56,150 --> 00:39:57,690
the Zornia case comes first.

869
00:39:57,690 --> 00:39:58,750
I understand that.

870
00:39:59,910 --> 00:40:01,060
But is Yan Nanxing

871
00:40:01,100 --> 00:40:03,100
more important than our family now?

872
00:40:08,580 --> 00:40:10,090
I had no choice.

873
00:40:19,170 --> 00:40:19,720
What does

874
00:40:20,270 --> 00:40:21,210
Nan Jifeng leaving

875
00:40:21,210 --> 00:40:22,740
have to do with Yan Nanxing?

876
00:40:23,850 --> 00:40:25,180
Of course it's related.

877
00:40:25,530 --> 00:40:27,130
She and Mother are in a fight.

878
00:40:27,290 --> 00:40:28,010
What if she

879
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:28,970
spouts nonsense

880
00:40:29,550 --> 00:40:30,510
outside

881
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,430
about us hiding

882
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:32,710
an imperial criminal?

883
00:40:32,710 --> 00:40:34,310
You keep everything from me.

884
00:40:34,470 --> 00:40:35,610
Even Yan Nanxing knows

885
00:40:35,610 --> 00:40:36,340
more than me.

886
00:40:37,990 --> 00:40:39,170
Yan Nanxing will never

887
00:40:39,170 --> 00:40:40,290
hurt anyone

888
00:40:40,740 --> 00:40:42,310
for her own selfish reasons.

889
00:40:42,310 --> 00:40:43,470
Why are you so sure

890
00:40:43,670 --> 00:40:44,950
she won't betray us?

891
00:40:45,350 --> 00:40:46,190
Just because

892
00:40:46,210 --> 00:40:47,270
she was once your woman?

893
00:40:47,270 --> 00:40:47,750
Yes.

894
00:40:48,350 --> 00:40:49,790
Because she's my woman.

895
00:40:50,200 --> 00:40:51,080
I trust her.

896
00:40:54,910 --> 00:40:56,390
I'm afraid you're blinded

897
00:40:56,420 --> 00:40:57,220
by love.

898
00:40:58,990 --> 00:41:00,650
Things only turned out like this

899
00:41:00,650 --> 00:41:02,380
as you offended Mother for her.

900
00:41:03,790 --> 00:41:05,850
So you couldn't tell right from wrong

901
00:41:06,150 --> 00:41:07,210
and drove her away?

902
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:09,550
That was Mother's order.

903
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:10,570
As a child,

904
00:41:10,730 --> 00:41:11,830
it's natural to share

905
00:41:11,830 --> 00:41:13,030
their parents' burdens.

906
00:41:13,030 --> 00:41:14,080
It's filial piety.

907
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:15,920
But if our parents are in the wrong,

908
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,720
we should point out the mistakes

909
00:41:18,180 --> 00:41:19,390
instead of letting them be a laughingstock

910
00:41:19,390 --> 00:41:20,230
by defending

911
00:41:20,390 --> 00:41:21,850
their so-called dignity.

912
00:41:22,270 --> 00:41:23,930
This is the real filial piety.

913
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:25,390
You have your reasons

914
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:27,150
and I have my reasons.

915
00:41:27,270 --> 00:41:28,070
Your reasons?

916
00:41:30,310 --> 00:41:31,910
Let's put aside Yan Nanxing.

917
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:34,970
You asked Shang Bieli to take away Nan Jifeng.

918
00:41:35,150 --> 00:41:37,470
Ruling out your suspicion of Yan Nanxing,

919
00:41:37,470 --> 00:41:38,930
what logic warrants that?

920
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:39,870
I told you.

921
00:41:40,950 --> 00:41:42,260
This is the best-case scenario

922
00:41:42,260 --> 00:41:43,050
for General Nan

923
00:41:43,050 --> 00:41:44,170
and our family.

924
00:41:45,430 --> 00:41:46,890
I have a clear conscience.

925
00:41:47,350 --> 00:41:48,480
A clear conscience?

926
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:51,310
Suoluo.

927
00:41:52,310 --> 00:41:53,150
You always say

928
00:41:53,590 --> 00:41:54,760
I'm the one endangering

929
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:55,910
our family.

930
00:41:56,940 --> 00:41:58,670
But have you ever thought about

931
00:41:59,230 --> 00:42:00,580
how your actions

932
00:42:01,080 --> 00:42:02,630
are really trapping our family

933
00:42:02,630 --> 00:42:03,430
in injustice?

934
00:42:06,890 --> 00:42:09,800
Benevolence, justice, loyalty, bravery.

935
00:42:10,470 --> 00:42:12,070
This is our ancestral motto.

936
00:42:14,030 --> 00:42:16,950
The Jiangs have earned great military merits for generations.

937
00:42:16,950 --> 00:42:18,030
It's not for honor

938
00:42:19,030 --> 00:42:20,230
but for the country

939
00:42:20,790 --> 00:42:21,790
and the people.

940
00:42:23,450 --> 00:42:24,730
As a Jiang descendant,

941
00:42:25,550 --> 00:42:26,870
if you only care about our family's

942
00:42:26,870 --> 00:42:28,130
safety and interests,

943
00:42:28,610 --> 00:42:29,670
you'll truly be

944
00:42:29,670 --> 00:42:31,270
letting our ancestors down.

945
00:42:32,710 --> 00:42:34,300
Be it investigating Zornia

946
00:42:34,690 --> 00:42:36,050
or saving Nan Jifeng,

947
00:42:36,870 --> 00:42:37,990
I've lived up

948
00:42:37,990 --> 00:42:39,550
to our ancestral

949
00:42:39,550 --> 00:42:40,270
motto.

950
00:42:41,470 --> 00:42:42,530
But what about you?

951
00:42:43,750 --> 00:42:44,810
What have you done?

952
00:42:49,810 --> 00:42:50,800
To think you're

953
00:42:50,950 --> 00:42:52,810
Imperial Academy's chancellor.

954
00:42:53,460 --> 00:42:54,190
Suoluo.

955
00:42:55,260 --> 00:42:56,890
You've really let me down.

956
00:43:01,040 --> 00:43:03,170
His Majesty conferred the title on me.

957
00:43:03,240 --> 00:43:05,700
It's not up to you whether I deserve it or not.

958
00:43:10,990 --> 00:43:12,280
I have work to do.

959
00:43:12,670 --> 00:43:13,230
Goodbye.

